## üñº Image Features

- Upload up to **15 images** at once (Premium: unlimited)  
- Supported formats: **JPG, PNG, WebP, AVIF, HEIC, TIFF**  
- Edit mode: apply changes to **all images** or **current image**  
- Tools:
  - Crop (1:1, 4:3, 16:9, etc.)  
  - Rotate & flip  
  - Adjust brightness, contrast, saturation, sharpness, temperature  
  - Auto-correction  
  - Reset adjustments  
- Watermark:
  - Text or image watermark  
  - Custom size, opacity, and position  

