## ‚öôÔ∏è Optimization Settings

- Quality control (recommended: **60‚Äì80%**)  
- Output formats: **JPEG, PNG, WebP, AVIF**  
- Max width: choose from **640‚Äì1920px** or keep original  
- Auto-optimize on upload  
- Extra options:  
  - Progressive JPEG  
  - Remove metadata (EXIF, GPS)  
